Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We and the Roman Catholic Church jump into the whirlpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we meet, Tatemiya Saiji speaks of an unbelievable truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the fate of Orsola is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "The Amakusa Church."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross, the story begins.
